data.description: House Hack Opportunity - Here is your chance to live in one of Ocala's most exclusive and well-established neighborhoods at an amazing price.  The roof is 2020, the HVAC is 2018, and the location is Lemonwood I near Sherwood Hills.  This 3/2 POOL home with a 2 car garage and an ADDITIONAL detached garage / workshop is situated on 1.17 acres near the end of winding a cul-de-sac road with other spacious and uniquely designed homes on larger lots surrounded by mature vegetation. This home already has some great features including a fenced back yard, fire place, granite countertops, a soaring tongue in groove rough cut cedar ceiling, a living / game room AND a great room, 2 walk-in closets, floor to ceiling windows overlooking the pool, and NO CARPET.  What it needs is your vision and TLC - start with paint and removing the popcorn ceiling and go from there - as much or as little as you want.  Let your imagination go wild - this is a neighborhood where it would be hard to over-improve - just check out the neighboring properties.  They say you can change everything about a house but the location - so bring your designs and dreams, add them to the great bones and updates of this potentially amazing home in an already amazing neighborhood.  NO HOA.
